
                            <%inherit file="perspective_template.mako"/>
                            <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; line-height: 21pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">最近因辅导孩子做作业，父母心衰力竭的场景一再显现，陪读爸妈相继沦陷，从单打到混合双打，模式不断更新，结果却仍是一把辛酸泪。妈妈们上得厅堂，下得厨房，一到辅导孩子作业全部歇菜；爸爸们外面事业风光无限，前呼后拥，回家辅导作业照样爆缸。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: SimSun; color: #f87a7a;">我们先来回顾一下妈妈们的表现</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><img src="../static/article_images/image_25931905721618082562229.png" width="624" height="620" /></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">战在陪读第一线的妈妈们来说</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">咆哮只是开胃小菜</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">这场很漫长很漫长很漫长的煎熬</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">才刚刚开始</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">每次陪孩子写作业都是一次修行，唐僧取经还有三个徒弟一匹马，九九八十一难就能结束了。而陪读之路看不见尽头啊！</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">陪孩子读书就是在一个看不见边界的大海上，你开着小船带着孩子一起渡海，能让你坚持不把他扔下去的唯一理由就是亲生的了</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">!</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: SimSun; color: #f87a7a;">我们再来看看爸爸们的状态</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">岳云鹏的妻子曾晒出他给女儿辅导作业时，哭笑不得、如坐针毡、崩溃至极的搞笑表情。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><img src="../static/article_images/image_27051408831618082562234.png" width="625" height="516" /></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">绝望之中，岳云鹏只能公开招聘家教：「条件都好说，能辅导我闺女的作业都可以！」</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">有些老父亲性情本温柔，但也奈何不了陪娃写作业的暴怒与哀愁，后爹模式全新上线。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">前</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">30年没着过的急，全跟作业杠上了。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">前</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">30年没发过的脾气，全撒在孩子身上了。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">喊声、叫声、咆哮声，声声如雷贯耳，杀气十足。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">我朋友说，他每次辅导孩子写作业，家里的狗都绕着他走。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: SimSun; color: #f87a7a;">陪读下的常见病症</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">在加拿大，尽管孩子学习没有国内那么多作业，但华裔家长对孩子教育向来要求较高，课后补习也是层出不穷。很多家长甚至放弃国内舒适的生活条件和满意的工作，专心陪娃读书。考私校、考名校的压力下，很多陪读家长也是大呼崩溃。我们一起来梳理一下陪读后遗症，请各位陪读家长对号入座。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;"><br /><br /></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">妈妈们的常见病症如下：</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">1. 乳腺增生；</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">2. 内分泌失调；</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">3. 甲状腺囊肿；</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">4. 高血压；</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">5. 卵巢早衰；</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">6. 脑溢血；</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">7. 焦虑抑郁。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;"><br /><br /></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: 21pt; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">爸爸们的常见病症：</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">1. 高血压</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">2. 脱发、失眠</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">3. 甲状腺囊肿</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">4. 焦虑抑郁</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">5. 痔疮</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">6. 性功能障碍&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">这些疾病如果不得到有效治疗，发展下去可能就会成为重疾，这不，有爸爸因为辅导孩子做作业结果心梗住院了。不少朋友戏谑道：<strong><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;">不买重疾险，还敢辅导孩子做作业？</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: SimSun; color: #f87a7a;">加拿大的重疾险能够保障什么？</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">重疾险，通常是投保人为自己购买的一种让自己受益的保险。就保障内容来说，包括癌症、心脏冠状动脉（搭桥）手术、突发性心脏病、中风、脑退化（老年痴呆症）、细菌性脑膜炎、主动脉手术、良性脑肿瘤、失明、昏迷、失聪、心瓣置换、肾衰竭、断肢、丧失说话能力、主要器官移植、主要器官衰竭（轮候移植）、运动神经疾病、多发性硬化、因工受伤引致丧失免疫力病毒（</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">HIV）、瘫痪、柏金逊症、严重烧伤、丧失独立生活能力等二十多种。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">当受保人被确诊患了保险合约中所定义的受保疾病时，并度过一定的存活等候期，即可一次性获得等同于所购保额的保险赔偿金，且这笔赔偿完全免税。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">在加拿大如果选择保终身的重疾险，往往是可以退保费的，也就是所有交的保费可以拿回来，用于退休养老或者最后一笔费用，相当于用利息做了一份保障，相当划算。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">通常重疾险保单中还包括早期疾病的理赔。也就是说，保险公司通常会支付一笔额外的</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">15%到25%的重疾险保额的赔偿，通常最高不超过5万。这些疾病包括：</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">冠状动脉成形术、乳腺导管原位癌、早期慢性淋巴细胞白血病、早期前列腺癌、早期甲状腺癌、肠胃基质肿瘤、第一级神经内分泌肿瘤、浅层恶性黑色素。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">需要强调的是，早期赔付是保险公司额外赠送的，不影响主险的理赔。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: SimSun; color: #f87a7a;">投保故事</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">最近听说了几个妈妈的投保故事，不禁为这些陪读妈妈感到惋惜：</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">Linda的孩子今年上十一年级，因为孩子的成绩不理想，自身焦虑引起甲状腺功能紊乱反而情绪更加急躁，因担心自己未来健康想买保险，结果保险公司的答复是，可以承保，但是有例外情况，即不承保甲状腺癌。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">Sammy因为辅导孩子做作业导致高血压，一直没有意识到这个身体问题。在申请重疾险安排体检的时候才发现这个问题，保险公司直接做出了拒保的决定，要求Sammy将血压稳定控制后，方可考虑承保。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; color: #7f7f7f;">陪读的爸妈真心不容易，还听说有些家长因为孩子没有达到自己的预期，怀疑自己来加拿大的意义，怀疑自己的选择，最后导致焦虑抑郁的。为了孩子，请关爱自己，从一份重疾险开始！最后再啰嗦一句，保险真的不是一件想买就能买到的产品，重疾险更是保险中的&ldquo;奢侈品&rdquo;！！</span></p>